vector_to_search = rng.random((1, DIM), np.float32)
expr = f"10 <= {AGE} <= 25"
valid_ids = [1, 12, 123, 1234]

def external_filter_func(hits: Hits):

    collection_name=collection_name,

    batch_size=100,
    anns_field=PICTURE,

    external_filter_func=external_filter_func,
    output_fields=[USER_ID, AGE]
)
